

Parallel NVE simulation on 6 processors, 12000 steps, log info to screen:

   mpirun -np 6 ddSim -e -p param.nve -c commands

To postprocess the resulting config and trajectory files:

   mdPp -p param.pp -c commands.pp

To restart the simulation and continue to 25000 steps

   mpirun -np 6 ddSim -e -r restart -c commands.rst

